Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.91,0:00:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Kousei! Don't\Ncry over a skinned knee!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.87,0:00:12.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're a man, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.58,0:00:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me! My ankle went\N"snap!" That's right, "snap!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.67,0:00:17.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:21.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for\Nmaking me do the...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.09,0:00:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.64,0:00:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But thank goodness\Nyou only hurt your leg.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.93,0:00:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I'd gotten your hands hurt, I\Nwould've gotten killed by your mom.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:41.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop crying, dummy Kousei!\NYou're making me cry...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.13,0:02:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here. A towel and a\Nchange of clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.34,0:02:24.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put your uniform in the dryer.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.63,0:02:30.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My dad's away on business a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.26,0:02:35.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's bigger than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.20,0:02:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There you are. Is coffee okay?\NI can make you some hot milk, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What...what the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:12.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, okay? Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.64,0:03:15.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.56,0:03:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.48,0:03:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wholesome playing starts\Nwith a wholesome environment!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:26.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First order of business -\Ncleanup! Air this place out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're next door, Tsubaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:32.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not what it looks like!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.87,0:03:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a good reason for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:34.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kao-chan?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In Kousei's clothes? With wet hair?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.86,0:03:40.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.88,0:03:52.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She sure is fired\Nup, that Tsubaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.30,0:03:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't she just\Non a rampage?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.39,0:03:56.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess false cheer is\Nbetter than none at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.48,0:04:07.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:10.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! What you just\Nplayed - on tape!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.40,0:04:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your set piece is Chopin's\NÉtude Op. 25 No. 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.74,0:04:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:20.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The tempo and sound are\Nso out of sync! This isn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.25,0:04:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He sucks, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.46,0:04:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Competing like this? I'm backing out!\NThat's right, if I act now I can still...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:29.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've already sent in your submission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.96,0:04:31.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that my wallet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.72,0:04:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what kind of competition is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.55,0:04:36.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Maihou Music Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A national-level contest that's\Nspawned many a renowned musician.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.77,0:04:45.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you win Nationals, you might even\Nget the chance to perform overseas!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.07,0:04:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What Kao-chan's saying sounds like\N something from a faraway, different world...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.66,0:04:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to study under some teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.70,0:04:59.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Face it. This is a challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:03.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna prove that you can\Nplay even if you can't hear the notes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"It takes courage to sail\Nin uncharted waters!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.75,0:05:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Snoopy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.63,0:05:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.26,0:05:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Woof!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:14.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The important thing is your imagery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Before your fingers touch the keys,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.93,0:05:21.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you must determine in your mind\Nhow you're going to play it."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:23.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Anton Rubinstein.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.06,0:05:26.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you play the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is it for your own sake?\NFor someone else's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.69,0:05:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How do you want to play this piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.36,0:05:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How does the real you\Nwant to play Chopin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.33,0:05:40.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So anyway, I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You two take it from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! You stink of sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.21,0:05:45.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna work hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:46.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Our break will be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.67,0:05:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:52.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.21,0:05:56.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So it's just you and me again, huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chopin... Is that\NKou-chan playing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.61,0:06:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so he started playing again?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:17.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Should I take a snack over to him, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:23.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's your mental image?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.58,0:06:25.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A horse-drawn carriage
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.87,0:06:26.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unoriginal! Lack of imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,over cobblestones in Europe...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:29.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Image?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.67,0:06:31.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sunny-side up eggs for breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mundane! Unromantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Image!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.05,0:06:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Image.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.64,0:06:40.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Image.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:42.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Image.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:46.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is an image, anyway?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:50.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is it different than how\Nyou interpret the music?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:53.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How do you want to play this piece?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:56.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How do I want to...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...play this piece?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.51,0:07:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.23,0:07:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as she's quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.75,0:07:56.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How are Regionals going?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.34,0:08:00.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We've never been readier. The only\Nthing I'm afraid of is injury.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.13,0:08:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How about you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The other day Arima-kun had\Nsmoke coming out of his ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.76,0:08:07.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll actually be visible soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.06,0:08:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think he might be\Npushing himself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:15.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, he was kind\Nof reeling in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:20.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do want him to play the piano.\NBut I don't want him to suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, Arima-kun is trying\Nto turn that suffering into notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.24,0:08:32.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exposing both his pain and his suffering,\Neven his own struggling self...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.21,0:08:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how he'll come to\Ndwell inside his music.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how we play\Nmusic that's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:43.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima-kun is in the middle\Nof doing that. I'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.51,0:08:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.76,0:08:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so supportive\Nof Kousei, Kao-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'd have to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.19,0:09:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's like a hopeless\Nkid brother, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.45,0:09:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:10.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...isn't hopeless at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:15.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.38,0:09:17.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.36,0:09:46.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way\Nhome from practice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.49,0:09:49.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was wondering what you were up to.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.03,0:09:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way home now, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:55.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're always heading home at\Nthe same time these days, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:58.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tsubaki?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.25,0:10:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that we...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...there's no me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? What's that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.51,0:10:08.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.51,0:10:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we... go out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.14,0:10:18.15,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Music Preparation Room
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:23.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How do I want to play this\Npiece of music, I wonder?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:25.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:27.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.16,0:10:31.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who do I want to play it for?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.20,0:10:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you pack it in for today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.12,0:10:38.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally dark outside.\NThe moon's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.58,0:10:40.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:46.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you resent me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.05,0:10:51.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Something Tsubaki-chan said.\NThat you're suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've known that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.52,0:11:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I realized it when I saw your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to hear your music,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you try to abandon the piano...\NEven as you cling to it for support.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:10.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why, as if you're\Nturning your back on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.41,0:11:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you try to hide it under dust and books.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.58,0:11:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You love it, but you can't go near it.\NYou miss it, but you can't touch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're grieving,\Nthough you're hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.33,0:11:23.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I pretend that I don't see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.80,0:11:30.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Play the piano!" "Work hard at it!"\NIrresponsible things like that - that's all I say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're suffering because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.97,0:11:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.23,0:11:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was you who swept\Naway all that dust.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.82,0:11:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I look like I'm suffering,\Nhuh? That's not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.24,0:11:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But of course I'd be suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.53,0:11:55.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, I'm gonna sail in\Nuncharted waters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.91,0:12:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Both taking on a challenge, and\Ncreating something, is painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's fulfilling. So thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:09.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My world had already\Nchanged long ago.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's just that I never realized it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.43,0:12:17.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For sweeping away the dust\Nthat had collected on my body...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.06,0:12:18.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.52,0:12:22.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For encountering me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.73,0:12:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ever since that day, my world...\Neven the keyboard...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:30.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}became colorful...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.95,0:12:39.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You stink...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The girl that my best friend likes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.13,0:12:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As if we're hiding\Nfrom the silver moon,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:51.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the two of us in this music room,\Nin the middle of the night...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's like there's no one in the world but us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.97,0:12:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, we will now begin\Nthe rally for Regionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.27,0:13:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let's hear how\Npumped up—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.60,0:13:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What lucky boys you are to\Nhave been born in this era!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:12.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're going to be there\Nwhen a star named Ryota Watari is born!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.53,0:13:15.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you all,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:21.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a good time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.33,0:13:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, let's start over. Next...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.08,0:13:28.34,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Music Preparation Room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lame.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:36.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.80,0:13:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Average.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pedestrian.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.35,0:13:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I can see you've got\Nthe set piece down pat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.89,0:13:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can play the sheet music\Nperfectly, it doesn't change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.27,0:13:49.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Chopin's whispering to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Where are you in all this?"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.29,0:14:01.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.58,0:14:05.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we go cheer at Regionals?\NFor a change of scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:10.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass on that. I'll only be the\Nsame as before if I leave it like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.00,0:14:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to transcend perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.76,0:14:14.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing doing. We're gonna go cheer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you shut yourself up\Nin here, you'll suffocate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.31,0:14:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Musicians need time to gaze up at the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:32.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Last inning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tighten up the defense in the hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.40,0:14:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let anything get through!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.36,0:14:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:39.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you, Tsubaki.\NIf we don't at least tie it up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.78,0:14:41.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.83,0:14:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:48.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.01,0:14:55.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Play ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.22,0:14:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A famous violinist once said...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:00.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Music transcends words."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.72,0:15:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.06,0:15:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:07.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By exchanging notes, you\Nget to know one another,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:08.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to understand one another.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.65,0:15:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ball!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.27,0:15:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Let's go, Triple Crown champ!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.31,0:15:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As if your souls were connected,\Nand your hearts were overlapping.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.94,0:15:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Don't miss any meatballs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.28,0:15:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a conversation through instruments.\NA miracle that creates harmony.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.41,0:15:26.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that moment, music transcends words.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:29.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's awful?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:31.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Making a girl carry\Nhim on her shoulders!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.17,0:15:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, but girls are\Nbigger during childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:38.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point! I'm\Ntalking about a maiden's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But even though\Nhe's normally hopeless,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,he's amazing when\Nhe plays the piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.60,0:15:47.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, the other day\Nhe got a standing ovation...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.31,0:15:50.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Did I say something funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:52.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's always the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're always going on\Nand on about Arima-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.36,0:15:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Through the gap!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, Tsubaki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.91,0:16:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't like this, I don't\Nlike this, I don't like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.74,0:16:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sure, I know. That I have\Nno right to be feeling this way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.16,0:16:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I still don't like it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just don't like it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.59,0:16:16.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We were always together.\NI was always by his side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:20.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}During times of joy,\Nand of grief as well.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.55,0:16:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I realize he's faraway\Nfrom me now...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.80,0:16:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not by his side...\NThere's somebody else there...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:31.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What the...! Tsubaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.77,0:16:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:33.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.77,0:16:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't like this! Look at me!\NLook at me, will you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.07,0:16:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not with those eyes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:41.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't look at someone else!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:48.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ballgame!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki, I'm going home this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you live over there, Kashiwagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let your boyfriend console you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.10,0:17:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.19,0:17:17.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sen...pai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.70,0:17:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.92,0:17:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei... this is embarrassing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.43,0:17:47.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, no one's looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.55,0:17:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But nobody else was onto me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and how long have\Nwe known each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.35,0:17:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Kao-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.65,0:18:01.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She went home. She said,\N"Go to Tsubaki-chan by yourself."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.61,0:18:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After that roll down the hill, you carried\Nme like this, even though you were hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:11.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And then your own ankle\Nswelled up like a handball, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.37,0:18:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.08,0:18:17.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed at\Nall since we were kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.58,0:18:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:22.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My heart is always wavering.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.88,0:18:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice try. But I know\Neverything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.51,0:18:28.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you never have to\Nhold back with me, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've always made you\Nworry so much about me,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:39.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I wish you'd let me\Nworry about you once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.02,0:18:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I might be a flaky kid brother,\Nbut I'm gonna try hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:49.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna try hard. So...\NI want the happy Tsubaki to watch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:54.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because it would be too lame\Nto ride on your shoulders forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I gotta say...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.71,0:19:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're lighter than\Nyou look, huh, Tsubaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.54,0:19:02.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you are a girl, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.67,0:19:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's that supposed\Nto mean? That's so weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.47,0:19:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, that was\Na weird thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.97,0:19:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The seasons... might\Nbe about to change...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Who cares about music?\NWho cares about words?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have the long, long time\Nthat we've spent together,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and we have so many\Ntiny, precious memories.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.24,0:19:31.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.07,0:19:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time, I'll give you\Na piggyback ride, okay?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:44.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We lost! We freakin'\Nlost because of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.72,0:19:53.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,After we all fought so hard!\NI'm so bitter, I'm so bitter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:20:00.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I'm bitter over\Nlosing, even though I'm depressed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.02,0:20:03.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}My ankle's killing me!\NWe lost the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.81,0:20:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even though my ankle hurts, and\Nmy eyes are smeared with tears...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.44,0:20:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I've never felt worse..{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.86,0:20:12.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder why the stars\Nare sparkling like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The scent of the music room in his hair.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:19.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can hear his slightly ragged breathing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.12,0:20:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His shoulder, wet\Nwith tears, is so warm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.63,0:20:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am by his side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:29.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish time would just stand still.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the list of Maihou contestants.\NCheck out the flagged name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.69,0:20:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It'll get you fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.98,0:20:50.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for two whole years.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now it's time for me to get revenge\Nfor all those years of humiliation!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.16,0:20:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see you already know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.20,0:20:59.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.50,0:21:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No use playing dumb.\NYou sound so animated.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.17,0:21:05.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're just imagining things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been wondering what you were up to,\N and now you've finally shown up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just you wait, I'm gonna wipe up\Nthe floor with you next time!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.43,0:21:16.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kousei Arima\NSumitani Junior Highschool
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.39,0:21:17.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei Arima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.93,0:21:19.93,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,On the Way Home
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.93,0:21:21.93,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,
